Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.88,0:00:23.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.39,0:00:29.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.05,0:00:35.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.52,0:00:43.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然  充滿疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.70,0:00:51.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起度過每一天 直到將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.91,0:00:58.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流著眼淚  無法釋懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.67,0:01:09.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想請教  如何追回失去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.76,0:01:16.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.48,0:01:22.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.07,0:01:28.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.25,0:01:33.09,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把謎團解開吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.48,0:21:58.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&Hc8\3a&Hc8\4a&Hc8}為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.52,0:22:05.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.86,0:22:14.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此淒涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.83,0:22:21.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.33,0:22:30.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.97,0:22:39.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.35,0:22:47.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.61,0:22:57.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.70,0:23:06.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.34,0:00:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 閃耀的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.35,0:00:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天講的是雪女的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人心也冰冷的悲慘事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.40,0:00:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.81,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女傳說殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.18,0:01:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肉體就算毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的魂魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.74,0:01:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會與白雪同時復活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.93,0:02:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的演技實在是太逼真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.24,0:02:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過做得還挺逼真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西挺稀奇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.19,0:02:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不久前到這兒投宿的房客所留下來的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.59,0:02:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛才看了電視演的雪女吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得真的好怕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是世界上根本沒有什麼雪女嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.98,0:02:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡從以前就一直以雪女經常在附近出沒而聞名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.24,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女就會出現哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的要住在這兒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅館哪裡好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是除了這裡也沒有別的地方可住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在公車又走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.18,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前幾天打電話預約過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是木下明子小姐和淺沼洋子小姐對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走了這麼遠的路到這兒可不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想你們也差不多該到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才好像在說木下明子小姐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.98,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才還在電視上看了你演的那出雪女之戀的電視劇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是女明星木下明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.85,0:03:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.85,0:03:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.38,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在最後跳到湖裡面去的那一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演得真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.67,0:03:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是一條直線似的就跳到湖裡面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實跳下湖的並不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洋子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個替身演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些在危險的時候代替主角演出的人對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子是我自己專職的替身演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 她也等於是我的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 洗手間在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣實在是太冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳順著走廊走到盡頭 左手邊就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以住那間有柿子樹的房間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 您喜歡就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 去睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個洋子小姐說她是第一次到這個地方來對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 她怎麼會知道洗手間在什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.94,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你的好奇心還真不是普通的旺盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間啊 我想搭蓋的方法或是位置應該是固定的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼古老的房子更是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要能夠放晴就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.99,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 雪女出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女出現了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能 明明在那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛親眼看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 大呼小叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半個人也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是妳老在想著那些恐怖情節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會把在雪地上面的雪塊看成雪女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天傍晚就會回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候全身按摩和做臉就要麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先跟你說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子 戴這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子還真像銀行搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做演員的最怕曬太陽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洋子和明子她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家說山上的氣候瞬息萬變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到說下雪就下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐 妳一個人回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子說她自己還想再滑一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐真是活力充沛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實她只是裝成那個樣子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上她的身體狀況並不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.16,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐身體不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是哪裡不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確叫人擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.53,0:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子她回來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是感冒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.17,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你們幫忙我省事多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.05,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐剛才還在咳嗽 她還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她好像沒有什麼食慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在房間休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘 現在能泡澡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八點以前都已經被你們包下來了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 你八點以後再洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.29,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟你就跟你叔叔一起去洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子 妳不要緊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是去看一下醫生比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再泡一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 你在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會洗好澡 你想不想一塊兒來喝杯小酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.86,0:09:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這次要演出舞臺劇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個實在太受歡迎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才從電視搬上舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有由明子擔任主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說洋子小姐也會演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 當然有我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定要來看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們當然會去看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.96,0:09:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 沒想到喝得這麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你去跟老闆拿幾瓶酒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經九點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你們也該睡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不反對威士忌的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.57,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我房裡有一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.96,0:09:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就再多喝一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就過去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就好好喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 威士忌呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像把它放到皮箱的最下面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子說她待會兒再幫我把酒拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.21,0:10:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 她還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次應該是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的威士忌來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天聊得實在是太痛快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 妳先去浴池好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回房去看一下明子的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.02,0:10:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才出來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這個娃娃應該不在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 會不會是喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐還沒來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.05,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是穿著一身雪白的雪女啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 明子她不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐她出了什麼事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你先看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是明子留下的遺書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺書？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到房間之後就沒有看到她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才到附近去找了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有找到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我仔細看過房間就發現了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來明子小姐她有肺癌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我只覺得咳得不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己也挺擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.90,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面說她得了跟她父親一樣的病症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說她父親就是因為肺癌病逝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她自己已經注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種現象叫做癌症過敏症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想像雪女一樣結束一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我剛才在浴池看到的雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是明子小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.93,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳立刻聯絡警方過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在天氣這麼冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得儘快把明子小姐找到才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也快點出去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去準備準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐本來已經預約去做美容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想自殺的人還會跟別人預約做臉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是她一時想不開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.74,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.82,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的話就回答一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.94,0:12:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現穿著一身雪女的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身冰冷的躺在雪地裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是木下明子小姐沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是跟她住在同一間旅館的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個有名的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三日町警署的川田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才在明子小姐的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現放了一瓶安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.25,0:13:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐把威士忌送來的時間是晚上十點多鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說她是在那之後自殺的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在浴池看到的雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該就是明子小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.48,0:13:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是我們發現屍體時拍下的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.62,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是自殺事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.72,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次似乎就沒有必要勞駕毛利名偵探了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹上有人爬過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.10,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這家旅館以前的主人現在住在哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的主人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.71,0:14:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在就住在我們隔壁的村子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到是你問這個幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事情想要請教他一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不是一件自殺事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且兇手就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在我們就將屍體送去做例行的解剖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這件案子應該是自殺不會有錯了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在絕對不能把這個屍體帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為木下明子小姐不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.83,0:15:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.33,0:15:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼證據說她是被人殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川田警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐的屍體發現時所拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你拿出來再仔細看一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時是被夾在她的和服領口裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個計畫在旅程中自殺的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會像她這樣粗心大意的穿衣服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.69,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定是別人替她把和服換上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺沼洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.43,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.77,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道明子小姐她的精神狀態可不能跟平常相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不認為她穿和服的時候會去注意她的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川田警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你仔細看看照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的屍體好像是被埋在很深的雪地下面對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我記得昨天的雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從傍晚五點開始下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了八點的時候就停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明子小姐是在昨天晚上十點之後才自殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.88,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的屍體應該不會被埋在那麼深的雪地裡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.85,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你仔細把明子小姐的臉看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的臉上還塗著防曬霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個在晚上自殺的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在臉上塗什麼防曬霜嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確臉上有防曬霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.65,0:16:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是在不知情的狀況下被人下了安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能做這種事的 洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了妳之外再也找不到別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上你們明明看到明子小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.79,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那個明子小姐是由妳所扮演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她扮的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話怎麼解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先邀請明子小姐來滑雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂下這家旅館的人是妳對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼選擇這家旅館呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要就是因為這裡最方便你進行一人分飾兩角的戲法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人分飾兩角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.68,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟明子小姐身材背影都很相像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是想殺了明子小姐以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.52,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還必須讓大家認為她還活著才能讓妳脫罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.99,0:17:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會特別選擇投宿這家旅館的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.79,0:17:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是洋子小姐她是第一次到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.72,0:17:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還在念書的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個冬天曾經在這家旅館打過工對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家旅館之前的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還很清楚的記著妳的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妳應該是昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滑雪場那裡讓明子小姐先喝了安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.81,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著妳就幫她換上了雪女的衣服埋進了地底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候剛好下起了雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了你一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.19,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻沒有計算到雪下了一陣子就停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.37,0:17:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.22,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到這裡的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.58,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳第一次說妳看到的那個雪女就是洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在雪地裡披著一件不容易引人注意的白色衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才好遮掩妳手上體積龐大的和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳拿著兩件雪女的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件是明子小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件是妳扮演替身的時候穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那天就是要去把其中一件埋在地底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是昨天傍晚的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳再把衣服挖出來幫明子小姐穿上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.02,0:18:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你又裝著什麼事都沒有發生的樣子回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是明子那天明明也回旅館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回到旅館之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就馬上假扮成明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓大家覺得她還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳利用了窗外的那棵柿子樹爬上了屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於替身演員的妳 這本就是家常便飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.01,0:18:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.18,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就把原先藏起來的明子小姐的滑雪用具給挖了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它拿在手上回到了旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著妳又為了讓我們聽到妳們的對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.84,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在露天浴池那裡一人分飾兩角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.45,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想憑妳要模仿明子小姐的聲音根本不難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的一件工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小蘭在浴池那裡看到的雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那就是妳在演出明子小姐自殺的一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.86,0:19:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做就是為了讓明子小姐看起來像要自殺的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.54,0:19:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓我們誤以為她在那個時候還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.53,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子她昨天幫我們拿來的威士忌怎麼解釋呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是妳自己演的獨角戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上我們根本就沒有看到明子小姐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.67,0:19:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個時候我明明拿回了一瓶威士忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.36,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說明子已經死掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說那瓶威士忌是誰拿來給我的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實妳會選在這家旅館還有另一個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的確是出去拿威士忌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.77,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那瓶酒卻是由傀儡娃娃送過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.42,0:20:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在我出去看的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有看到傀儡娃娃的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候非常的不巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就已經走到我的身後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳假裝要到洗手間去把娃娃又放回到臺子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.30,0:20:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是利用傀儡娃娃來代替明子小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那瓶威士忌酒瓶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該查不出任何明子小姐的指紋才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點就是證明她那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不在人世的最有力的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.47,0:20:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓明子喝下安眠藥之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她給殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺書也是我寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是明子的爸爸已經去世的事是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子她也沒有可以讓人挑剔的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我氣我一直以來都比不過明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.18,0:21:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在一開始的戲劇試演會上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比到決賽的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想到竟然輸給了明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後也一直如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.41,0:21:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每次都輸給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看著明子已經漸漸成為大明星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.59,0:21:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人常常會對我說這句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的確是長得像木下明子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這不是「超級明星臉」的節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.18,0:21:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次只要一想到明子存在一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.18,0:21:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只能永遠做她身後的影子就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪男出現了 雪男出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是佐知子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.24,0:23:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔在看風景的時候睡著了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.22,0:23:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.20,0:24:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔九點前都還是醒著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也跟佐知子一直在聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的不在場證明十分完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.17,0:24:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.98,0:24:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.39,0:24:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎約會殺人時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.53,0:24:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回叔叔有了大危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.65,0:24:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生這種事看他怎麼對媽媽交代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.79,0:24:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
